entries.femaleVariant: Performance is weak again, Luiz. Substandard. Not good at all.
But ma'am, can't you see I'm trying?. I work twenty hours a day, every day, no breaks...
Instead of trying, you should get some decent implants. Hausstocks, for instance.
But... it would take me fifty years to pay that off...
That is not the company's concern, Luiz.
